@startuml
title Abstract Factory - Ejemplo 1 - Implementacion Generica
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class Client {
    +run(): void
  }
  class FamilyAFactory {
    +createPrimary(): Primary
    +createSecondary(): Secondary
  }
  class FamilyAPrimary {
    +describe(): String
  }
  class FamilyASecondary {
    +describe(): String
  }
  class FamilyBFactory {
    +createPrimary(): Primary
    +createSecondary(): Secondary
  }
  class FamilyBPrimary {
    +describe(): String
  }
  class FamilyBSecondary {
    +describe(): String
  }
  interface FamilyFactory <<interfaz>> {
  }
  interface Primary <<interfaz>> {
  }
  interface Secondary <<interfaz>> {
  }
}

FamilyFactory <|.. FamilyAFactory
Primary <|.. FamilyAPrimary
Secondary <|.. FamilyASecondary
FamilyFactory <|.. FamilyBFactory
Primary <|.. FamilyBPrimary
Secondary <|.. FamilyBSecondary
Client ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
Client ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
Client ..> FamilyAPrimary : crea
Client ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyAFactory ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
FamilyAFactory ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
FamilyAFactory ..> FamilyAPrimary : crea
FamilyAFactory ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyAPrimary ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
FamilyAPrimary ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
FamilyAPrimary ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyASecondary ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
FamilyASecondary ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyBFactory ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
FamilyBFactory ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyBPrimary ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
FamilyFactory ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
FamilyFactory ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
FamilyFactory ..> FamilyAPrimary : crea
FamilyFactory ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
Primary ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
Primary ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
Primary ..> FamilyAPrimary : crea
Primary ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
Secondary ..> FamilyASecondary : crea
Secondary ..> FamilyBPrimary : crea
Secondary ..> FamilyAPrimary : crea
Secondary ..> FamilyBSecondary : crea
Main ..> Client : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
